# LinkedIn 2026 Format Arbitrage
**Expertise:** Format Arbitrage, Content Strategy, Niche Bending, LinkedIn 360 Brew Algorithm

This skill is designed to capture the structural "physics" of the late-2025/early-2026 LinkedIn algorithm (the "360 Brew" update). Organic reach has plummeted; the focus has shifted from surface-level engagement (likes) to depth (saves, dwell time, and multi-threaded comments from 2nd-degree connections). 

This skill translates deep strategic research into 5 specific deployable formats, prioritizing the "Costly Signaling" of authenticity and the "Commitment Escalation" of carousel frameworks. 

### Core 2026 Algorithmic Physics
1. **Dwell Time is the Currency:** Posts that generate 61+ seconds of dwell time achieve a 15.6% engagement rate. Formatting must encourage *time spent reading*.
2. **Saves > Likes:** Saves cause content to resurface. Frameworks and checklists (savable assets) crush hot takes (consumable assets).
3. **Conversation Depth:** Multi-threaded comments from 2nd-degree connections carry 2.6x more weight. The pinned comment strategy is mandatory.
4. **Coherence Creates Compounding:** Profile/content alignment is enforced. If the content doesn't match the headline expertise, distribution is suppressed. 
5. **Authenticity = Costly Signal:** In an AI-saturated feed, real photos in authentic work environments command premium trust.

### The 5 Active Arbitrage Formats (Refer to Prompts)
1. The Document Carousel (Apex Predator)
2. The Contextual Selfie (Costly Signal)
3. The Trapdoor Text Post (Curiosity Gap)
4. The Comment-to-Download Flywheel
5. The Self-Pinned Comment Strategy

### The 90-Day Sprint Directives
* **Profile Overhaul:** Headline formula (`[What you do] + [Who you do it for] + [Outcome]`), Featured section optimization (Lead Magnet + Booking Link ONLY, no descriptions).
* **Cadence (4-2-1):** 4-5 posts/week mixing formats. Rely on Signal Intelligence (trends breaking on X/Reddit) to determine topics.
* **The LinkedIn Hour:** 15m pre-post engagement (wake up graph), T-Zero publish + self-pin, 45m replying and engaging (30/30/30/10 split).
* **Offer Packaging:** Sell the *transformation* (Sovereignty/Time Reclaimed), never the technology (AI/Prompts). 
